        "subject": "LU-3791 hsm: don't copy attrs or xattrs in sanity-hsm",
        "message": "LU-3791 hsm: don't copy attrs or xattrs in sanity-hsm\n\nCopying attributes or extended attributes may fail on a shared NFS\nbackend (depending on the root squashing settings). So disable these\nfeature on the copytool command line in sanity-hsm.sh.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I33ae1a051005d1e69e4e6126078d22259af201a0\n"
